CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 18, 1949, pg. 21, reads: "Sweet Sixteen - Elayne Nelson entertained the above group of friends on her sixteenth birthday, June 4, at the home of her parents, Mr. and Mrs. Earl Nelson, 7039 Kedron Street. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of young men, including two in front wearing striped socks, and young women, gathered for sweet sixteen birthday party of Elayne Nelson, in living room of Nelson home, 7039 Kedron Street, Homewood
